#Control Statement :

* Conditional Control Statement (if, elif, else)
*Loop Control Statement (for, while)
--------------------------------------------------
# else if = elif

###Important Note :

*statement 1 -> if statement
*stetement 2 -> if statement, else statement
*stetement 3 or more -> if statement, elif statement..........., else statement

'''
if expretion :
        statement

elif expretion :
        statement

elif expretion :
        statement

elif expretion :
        statement
.
.
.
.
else :
        statement

'''


'''
print("Pass")
Print("Fail")
'''

#if statement : expression/condition - definitely True
#Example,

mark = 80
if mark>= 33:
    print("Pass")

if mark<33:
    print("Fail")
print("Program End")

#else statement : No expression/condition
#Example,

mark = 80
if mark>= 33:
    print("Pass")

else
    print("Fail")

#Even/Odd :   #if num%2==0 :
num =4
if num%2==0 :
    print("Even")

else:
    print("Odd")
